01:38:23,793 --> 01:38:27,883
Tapi, meski begitu kamu...

1143
01:38:28,963 --> 01:38:34,763
pasti akan senang.

1144
01:38:37,933 --> 01:38:39,933
Ketika Anda menjadi lebih tua.

1145
01:39:18,763 --> 01:39:20,013
Godou!

1146
01:39:23,393 --> 01:39:24,773
Tunggu!

1147
01:39:25,103 --> 01:39:26,023
Ada apa?

1148
01:39:26,813 --> 01:39:27,693
Apa?

