01:41:22,263 --> 01:41:24,353
pergi ke sisimu.

1161
01:41:31,903 --> 01:41:35,773
Mari kita bertemu lagi.

1162
01:41:40,783 --> 01:41:42,203
Lagi?

1163
01:41:48,743 --> 01:41:50,043
Miyo!

1164
01:41:59,383 --> 01:42:00,763
Kamu sangat bodoh.

1165
01:42:46,393 --> 01:42:47,223
Hei, kau baik-baik saja?

1166
01:42:48,513 --> 01:42:50,393
Seseorang!

1167
01:42:59,903 --> 01:43:00,983
Miyo!

1168
01:43:10,333 --> 01:43:11,953
Tuanku.

1169
01:43:19,423 --> 01:43:21,133
Aku ingin berada di sisimu.

1170
01:43:24,803 --> 01:43:26,593
Aku ingin tinggal bersamamu.

